    <string name="label_owm_weather_info">ℹ️ 90 minutes before each alarm, the short-term forecast\nfor the alarm time from the KMA National Climate Data Center\nand OpenWeatherMap is cross-validated and reflected here.\n\nForecasts can differ from actual weather,\nso the weather at the actual alarm time may not match.</string>
